'''Adam Meredith''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Bermuda Bowl]] (1) 1955 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (5) 1948, 1950, 1952, 1953, 1956 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (5)
** 0 (5) 1948, 1950, 1952, 1953, 1956 

===Runners-up===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (2) 1947, 1951 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (2)
** 0 (2) 1947, 1951 

